  archive_name: Stray
  archive_image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0ea4dbdfb96cdad46a646eab95da9e56, type: 3}
  islocked: 0
  description: 'Able to mimic any animal albeit with some deformities, common deformities
    are red eyes, exposed flesh, cold sores, and disfigured limbs. Often mimics Household
    pets and Livestock, but able to also take the form of wild animals.

'
  risk: Risk Level:Mid
  risk_bullets: '\u2022 Takes the form of any animal

    \u2022 Most often pets
    (cats, dogs, and livestock)

    \u2022 Will only eat the creature it mimics

'
  solution: Immediately Evacuate and Fortify once you realise the creature is following
    you (preferably an elevated surface if it's a land animal). Quiet your pet and
    wait for it to leave. Otherwise wait for the task force to arrive to dispose
    of the creature.
